  "texts": [
    "The ML model estimates of skin-friction drag show a decrease with increasing slope and fall quite well within previous laboratory measurements.",
    "It should also be noted that skin-friction drag measurements presented in figure 16 generally exhibit a large scatter when plotted against both wind speed and wave slope because, in part, the measurements in different studies were collected at different fetches.",
